[[Image:Nationallibrary.jpg|right|thumb|200px]] The '''National Library of the Kyrgyz Republic''' is the legal deposit and copyright agency for [[Kyrgyzstan]]. It was founded in 1934. It has a collection of 6 million documents in 89 languages from around the world. Since 2005 the head of the Kyrgyz National Library is Dr. Jyldyz Bakashova.
